The paper discusses the application of deep learning to non-factoid question answering, which is a subfield of natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which covers NLP and related topics. The paper also mentions various deep learning architectures, indicating a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Information retrieval (cs.IR) is also relevant as the paper discusses creating and releasing a QA corpus. Finally, neural networks (cs.NE) are mentioned as a technology used in the experiments.
